pageContext.claim: “'This is political malpractice. This is a horrible judgement call on the part of the Speaker. You put your members in Trump friendly districts in a very difficult spot. It's only going to extend it out further. This looks like the joke that it actually is.' Ben Domenech.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump purports to quote Domenech, but left out the section of the quote in which he said that lawmakers in Trump-friendly districts voted to impeach Trump.
